item.dc:creator: @MybBob MybBob
item.description:
@MybBob wrote:

Sorry to say this, but I’m going to give it 3/10, the reasons behind this are;

If your going to mess with the focal point, atleast try to make a improvement, the render is completely ruined, the background is workable, if you go for the abstract theme but you need to work on the flow from background to render / focal point, creating a unicen signature.

The text, COULD Be used to a advantage with a smaller size, and with a clipping mask above it, to make it flow a tiny bit more.
